1
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:15,079
I'll drink this cup of tea.

2
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:19,120
I know what you want to say.

3
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:23,200
Since you joined the company,

4
00:01:26,799 --> 00:01:28,719
you've poured tea for me for 20 years.

5
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:33,959
Chairman Zheng,

6
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:37,680
I'm not fit to stay by your side anymore.

7
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:39,359
Please just let me go.

8
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:44,079
You've always thought I wouldn't let you go,

9
00:01:44,319 --> 00:01:46,159
that I wouldn't give you a chance.

10
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,040
Is that right?

11
00:01:48,439 --> 00:01:49,599
You've been with me for 20 years.

12
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,959
My own son is only 18.

13
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:56,120
How could I bear to let you go?

14
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,959
I've always said I trust you,

15
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,799
so I've kept giving you chances.

16
00:02:01,799 --> 00:02:03,040
Not because I'm merciful,

17
00:02:04,959 --> 00:02:07,359
but because I see you as my own child.

18
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:11,599
Everyone needs a chance.

19
00:02:11,599 --> 00:02:12,400
I needed to give you one,

20
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:14,039
a chance to turn over a new leaf.

21
00:02:14,319 --> 00:02:15,840
Don't you understand even now?

22
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:18,120
This isn't just a simple mistake,

23
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:19,759
Han Lin,

24
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:22,080
where apologizing to me is enough.

25
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:25,000
I can forgive you a hundred times.

26
00:02:25,919 --> 00:02:27,199
But you broke the law.

27
00:02:27,879 --> 00:02:30,000
You must bear your own criminal liability.

28
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:34,319
Chairman Zheng, I know I was wrong.

29
00:02:34,319 --> 00:02:35,800
Please put in a word for me,

30
00:02:35,879 --> 00:02:37,719
give me a break, okay?

31
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,599
Han Lin,

32
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,479
this might be hard for you,

33
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,400
but take it like a man.

34
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,120
The lawyer will come find you.

35
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:56,000
You think I want to do this?

36
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,759
I've been by your side for 20 years.

37
00:02:58,759 --> 00:03:00,719
You just said it yourself, 20 years.

38
00:03:01,439 --> 00:03:02,879
Have you ever really seen me?

39
00:03:03,199 --> 00:03:05,000
Have you ever given me a chance to rise?

40
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:07,759
You only see Xiao Yifan and He Junjie.

41
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:09,479
You let them rise through the ranks.

42
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,319
And me?

43
00:03:10,319 --> 00:03:11,560
All I can do is stay by your side,

44
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,879
serving tea, bowing and scraping.

45
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,759
How am I any worse than them?

46
00:03:16,599 --> 00:03:17,879
You're not worse than them at all.

47
00:03:19,439 --> 00:03:21,159
Is a chance to rise more important,

48
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:23,240
or me keeping you out of prison?

49
00:03:23,719 --> 00:03:24,439
You know what?

50
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,360
That case from seven years ago,

51
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,439
I've known about it all along.

52
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:29,639
Why didn't I act back then?

53
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,759
Because I wanted to give you a chance.

54
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,520
You broke the law.

55
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,039
Don't other people's lives matter?

56
00:03:37,199 --> 00:03:39,240
Weren't those accidents real?

57
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,759
You'd do anything out of greed.

58
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,039
No.

59
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,400
You forced me into this.

60
00:03:47,319 --> 00:03:49,000
You forced me into all of it.

61
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,599
After all these years,

62
00:03:50,599 --> 00:03:52,639
I could easily have been a City Manager.

63
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,280
But you?

64
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,800
You insisted on keeping me by your side.

65
00:03:56,919 --> 00:03:58,840
How could I fulfill my ambitions?

66
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:03,520
You never saw any good in me.

67
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,360
I have many strengths.

68
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:09,439
But your eyes only see Xiao Yifan.

69
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,919
What does he even have?

70
00:04:12,159 --> 00:04:14,120
Didn't he just rely on your classmate,

71
00:04:14,199 --> 00:04:16,800
President Zhu's recommendation?

72
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,240
How is he better than me?

73
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:20,120
Tell me, how is he better than me?

74
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:21,839
Go on.

75
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:25,199
Chairman Zheng,

76
00:04:26,319 --> 00:04:27,040
I know,

77
00:04:27,399 --> 00:04:29,000
I can't escape this.

78
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,480
But

79
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,800
I've said my piece.

80
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,480
My conscience is clear.

81
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,519
You simply treat them better.

82
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,720
You never saw any good in me.

83
00:04:46,439 --> 00:04:47,120
It's all my fault,

84
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,199
right?

85
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:48,879
Yes.

86
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:50,000
Twenty years.

87
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,319
And you accuse me like this.

88
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:55,680
You think you wasted 20 years by my side.

89
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:56,680
Han Lin,

90
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:59,319
do you know how many years I've been in this industry?

91
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:02,399
Take a look.

92
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,800
Every building in Loujiang City,

93
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,439
I had a hand in building.

94
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,560
Every scar on my body

95
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:21,360
is a mark of my struggle.

96
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:24,120
Even now, you remain unrepentant.

97
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,040
Let me tell you something.

98
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,439
It's like

99
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:30,000
what a poet once said.

100
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,160
When you lack power,

101
00:05:32,959 --> 00:05:33,959
don't speak.

102
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:36,399
When you have power, you needn't speak.

103
00:05:36,519 --> 00:05:38,040
Everything is fair.

104
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,879
You just haven't given enough.

105
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:41,120
Don't you understand yet?

106
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,639
I wanted to give you one last chance.

107
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:44,199
Don't you get it?

108
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,240
But...

109
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,199
But in my eyes,

110
00:05:48,639 --> 00:05:49,439
what I see is...

111
00:05:49,439 --> 00:05:51,360
that you always thought I was worthless.

112
00:05:52,399 --> 00:05:54,279
You only ever had eyes for Xiao Yifan.

113
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,519
Isn't that right?

114
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,480
And him?

115
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,399
Him...

116
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:01,639
He got here thanks to President Zhu!

117
00:06:02,639 --> 00:06:03,399
Why him?

118
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,800
Why him, of all people?

119
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,360
Be a man.

120
00:06:11,439 --> 00:06:12,839
Take responsibility for your actions.

121
00:06:14,199 --> 00:06:15,519
Let me tell you one last thing.

122
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:17,879
Fate...

123
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:20,639
in Loujiang, isn't written in the stars.

124
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,240
Fate...

125
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:26,680
For many Loujiang people like me,

126
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,480
it's who holds on till the last second.

127
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,240
You still have a chance.

128
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,920
I have no chance left, Chairman Zheng.

129
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,959
I have no chance.

130
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,519
There's no chance anymore.

131
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,040
Chairman Zheng.

132
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:49,040
I'm sorry.

133
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,279
I'm sorry.

134
00:06:52,639 --> 00:06:54,000
I'm sorry.

135
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,600
Take care of yourself.

136
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:57,759
Take care.

137
00:06:58,959 --> 00:06:59,680
Han Lin.

138
00:07:01,319 --> 00:07:02,680
Take care of yourself in there.

139
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:05,040
Your position...

140
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:07,839
I'll keep it open for you.

141
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:13,160
Chairman Zheng.

142
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,920
I'll turn myself in.

143
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:25,519
Thank you.

144
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,840
Once Fang Bing gets out,

145
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,720
the two of you can tie the knot.

146
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:47,440
There's no chance for us.

147
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,679
Aren't you carrying Fang Bing's child?

148
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,159
Why aren't you showing yet?

149
00:08:57,799 --> 00:08:59,440
The truth is, I'm not pregnant.

150
00:09:01,519 --> 00:09:03,840
You're beautiful and well-educated.

151
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:06,320
Why be his mistress?

152
00:09:09,279 --> 00:09:10,639
I've already resigned.

153
00:09:10,919 --> 00:09:12,519
I'm leaving Loujiang City soon.

154
00:09:12,519 --> 00:09:13,559
And I'm never coming back.

155
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:15,600
Goodbye.

156
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:59,080
I've toiled in real estate for half my life.

157
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,200
Through decades of ups and downs.

158
00:10:03,399 --> 00:10:04,759
Every high-rise in this city,

159
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:06,759
I've watched rise with my own eyes.

160
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:10,000
I believe the spirit of this city is:

161
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,480
Fate isn't written in the stars.

162
00:10:15,519 --> 00:10:18,440
It's about who fights to the last second.

163
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:26,480
This is our golden age.

164
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:51,399
You ask me how deep my love is for you.

165
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:58,480
Go think about it, go take a look.

166
00:10:58,679 --> 00:11:03,320
The moon represents my heart.

167
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:17,840
One gentle kiss has touched my heart.

168
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:24,360
Grandma, when I grow up, I'll build

169
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,840
many tall, beautiful houses for you.

170
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:29,120
Wonderful, Grandma will wait for you.

171
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:43,519
You ask me how deep my love is for you.

172
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:51,000
Go think about it, go take a look.

173
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:55,799
The moon represents my heart.

174
00:11:57,720 --> 00:12:04,159
Go think about it, go take a look.

175
00:12:04,159 --> 00:12:09,399
The moon represents my heart.
